WEBVTT

00:02.135 --> 00:03.693
Previously on The Vampire Diaries:

00:03.870 --> 00:06.634
For over a century,
I have lived in secret until now.

00:06.806 --> 00:08.967
I know the risk,
but I have to know her.

00:09.142 --> 00:12.737
As a founding family member, it's my
duty to report some distressing news.

00:12.912 --> 00:15.005
- He's a Gilbert?
- Elena's uncle.

00:15.181 --> 00:17.649
Mayor Lockwood, is it?
My name is Pearl.

00:17.817 --> 00:20.217
- Hi.
- This is my daughter, Anna.

00:20.387 --> 00:24.221
Maybe there is such a thing as vampires.
They're just different.

00:25.592 --> 00:27.822
You got a problem with blood, Anna?

00:28.328 --> 00:32.526
The coroner's office has officially ruled
Vicki Donovan's death a drug overdose.

00:32.698 --> 00:35.167
- You don't think it was an overdose.
- Let it go.

00:35.335 --> 00:37.530
Is there something
you're not telling me?

00:39.339 --> 00:40.863
Take my wrist. You need blood.

00:41.441 --> 00:44.376
I have this hunger inside of me
that I've never...

00:44.544 --> 00:47.035
I've never felt before in my entire life.

00:47.213 --> 00:49.113
I don't want you to see me like this.

00:49.315 --> 00:51.909
I don't want you to know
that this side of me exists.

